column2: Shanghai Pudong Development Bank Co., Ltd. provides banking services. The Company provides loans, deposits, accounts settlement, foreign exchange, and other services. Shanghai Pudong Development Bank provides its services to individuals, companies, and other groups.

Guangzhou Baiyun International Airport Co.,Ltd. provides airport support services. The Company offers ground cleaning, airplane maintenance, airplane repairing, and other services. Guangzhou Baiyun International Airport also provides catering, space rental, advertising, and other services.
Dongfeng Automobile Co., Ltd. designs, manufactures, and markets diesel engines, light trucks, castings, and related spare parts.

China World Trade Center Co., Ltd. provides real estate services. The Company operates office building leasing business, shopping mall leasing business, apartment leasing business, hotel management business, and other related businesses. China World Trade Center offers services in China.

Beijing Capital Co.,Ltd offers water supply services. The Company provides water transmission, water system management, water network maintenance, and other services. Beijing Capital also operates environmental control, green resources development, and other businesses.

Shanghai International Airport Co., Ltd. operates Pudong Airport and Hongquiao airport in Shanghai.   The Company provides a full range of services including air traffic control, terminal management, cargo handling, advertising, space rental, and other related services.

Inner Mongolia BaoTou Steel Union Co.,Ltd smelts and processes ferrous metal products. The Company produces and sells steel plates, seamless metal tubes, heavy tubes, square steel, wire rods, steel pipes, steel scraps, and other related products. Inner Mongolia BaoTou Steel Union also provides importing and exporting services.

Huaneng Power International, Inc. provides electricity generation services. The Company offers electricity transmission, electricity distribution, power transformation, and other related services. Huaneng Power International provides services in China.
Anhui Expressway Co. Ltd. principally holds, operates and develops toll expressways and highways in Anhui province in China.

Huaxia Bank Co. Ltd. operates banking businesses. The Company offers deposits, loans, settlement, bill discounting, currency trading, bank guarantee, wealth management, and other banking services. Huaxia Bank provides services for enterprises and individuals.

China Minsheng Banking Corp., Ltd. operates commercial banking businesses. The Company provides deposit, loan, settlement, discount, financial bond issuance, government bond underwriting and trading, letter of credit, bank guarantee, and other related financial services. China Minsheng Banking offers services worldwide.

Rizhao Port Co.,Ltd. conducts port management and operation businesses. The company provides cargo warehousing, handling, transportation, and transit services. Rizhao Port provides port services for coal, cements, steel materials, minerals, and wood products.

Shanghai International Port (Group) Co., Ltd. offers port operation services. The Company provides cargo handling, port logistics, port commerce, pilotage, tugboat, shipping tally, and other port related services. Shanghai International Port (Group) provides services for worldwide customers.

Baoshan Iron & Steel Co., Ltd. manufactures and markets iron and steel products. The Company produces and sells cold rolled plates and coils, hot rolled plates and coils, seamless steel tubes, high-speed wire rods, steel billets, and other products. Baoshan Iron & Steel markets its products throughout China.

Henan Zhongyuan Expressway Company Limited operates expressway businesses. The Company provides toll highway investment, construction, and maintenance services. Henan Zhongyuan Expressway also conducts real estate development, oil distribution, and technology service businesses.

Shanghai Electric Power Company Limited operates power generation businesses. The Company generates electricity, thermal power, and other power products. Shanghai Electric Power also operates engineering contracting, new energy development, and other businesses.
Shandong Iron and Steel Company Ltd. manufactures and markets steel materials. The Company produces pig iron, steel billets, cast iron, and related products.

Zhejiang Zheneng Electric Power Co., Ltd. supplies electric power through operating thermal power generation.  The Company also involves in the research and development of electric power, power and energy-saving technology development, technical consulting, sales of energy-saving products, electrical engineering and asset management.

Huaneng Lancang River Hydropower Inc. provides hydropower generation services. The Company offers electricity transmission, electricity distribution, power transformation, and other related services. Huaneng Lancang River Hydropower also provides clean energy development services.

COSCO SHIPPING Energy Transportation Co., Ltd. offers marine shipping services. The Company provides refined oil transportation, crude oil transportation, and other services. COSCO SHIPPING Energy Transportation also ships iron ores, dry bulks, coal, and other products.

Huadian Power Internatioanal Corporation Limited operates electricity businesses. The Company provides power plant construction, hydropower, wind power, and solar power generation services. Huadian Power Internatioanal also conducts electricity transmission and distribution businesses.

China Petroleum & Chemical Corporation produces and trades petroleum and petrochemical products. The Company offers gasoline, diesel, jet fuel, kerosene, ethylene, synthetic fibers, synthetic rubber, synthetic resins, and chemical fertilizers. China Petroleum & Chemical markets its products throughout China.

China Southern Airlines Company Limited provides air transportation services. The Company offers passenger and freight air transportation services, aviation equipment maintenance and aircraft leasing services. Shanghai Airlines also provides ticket and hotel booking and consulting services. China Southern Airlines provides services worldwide.

CITIC Securities Co., Ltd. provides securities services. The Company provides securities brokerage, securities trading, securities underwriting, and other services. CITIC Securities also provides investment banking, asset management, investment consulting, and other services.

SANY Heavy Industry Co., Ltd manufactures and markets construction and engineering machinery and related parts. The Company produces and sells concrete pumps, concrete pump vehicles, road rollers, pavers, and other related products. Sany Heavy Industry markets its products worldwide.

Fujian Expressway Development Co., Ltd offers infrastructure construction services. The Company constructs highways and other infrastructures. Fujian Expressway Development also operates equipment leasing, construction investment, and other businesses.

Hubei Chutian Smart Communication Co.,Ltd. offers toll highway operation services. The Company provides highway and bridge investment, construction, and maintenance services. Hubei Chutian Smart Communication also manufactures and exports mobile intelligent communication terminals, mobile medical terminals, and car networking terminals.

China Merchants Bank Co., Ltd. operates as a commercial bank. The Company provides deposits, loans, wealth management, asset custody, finance leasing, investment banking, and other banking services. China Merchants Bank conducts businesses domestically and internationally.
Beijing Gehua CATV Network Co., Ltd. builds, manages, and maintains cable TV networks. The Company also provides advertising and information services.
AVIC Helicopter Co., Ltd. designs, develops, manufactures, and sells helicopters, airplane parts, and aviation-related products.  The Company also manufactures auto parts.

Sichuan Road & Bridge Co.,Ltd offers infrastructure construction services. The Company constructs roads, bridges, tunnels, and other engineering projects. Sichuan Road & Bridge also operates power generation businesses.

Poly Developments and Holdings Group Co., Ltd. operates real estate businesses. The Company provides real estate investment, estate development, brokerage, and real estate finance services. Poly Developments and Holdings Group also conducts cultural travel, convention, health care, and education businesses.

China United Network Communications Limited provides a variety of telecommunication services, including GSM and CDMA wireless telecommunication services, international and domestic long distance communication services, data communication and Internet services, as well as paging services.

Ningbo United Group Co., Ltd. is an investment holding company.  Through its subsidiaries, the Company operates in import/export trading, constructs infrastructure facilities, develops real estate, manufactures pharmaceuticals, and provides food services.
Zhejiang Guangsha Co., Ltd. develops real estate and undertakes construction projects.  The Company also provides travel services and operates in property management.

Kunwu Jiuding Investment Holdings CO.,Ltd engages in private equity investment. The Company invests in information technology, internet, healthcare, and other fields. Kunwu Jiuding Investment Holdings also operates real estate development and sales businesses.

Huangshan Tourism Development Co., Ltd. operates in the tourism industry.  The Company provides cableway transportation, sells garden tickets, operates hotels and restaurants, and provides tourism services.

Beijing Wandong Medical Technology Co., Ltd. manufactures and distributes medical equipment. The Company produces medical imaging equipment, X-rays equipment, high frequency digital gastrointestinal equipment, and resonance imaging machines. Beijing Wandong Medical Technology also provides veterinary imaging solutions and medical equipment maintenance services.

China Meheco Co Ltd operates an import and export business. The Company trades pharmaceutical products, paper making machinery, and aluminum extruders. CNTIC Trading also imports patent technologies and industrial techniques.

Xiamen Xiangyu Co., Ltd. provides logistics services. The Company offers logistics platform development, international transit, warehousing, and other services. Xiamen Xiangyu also operates import and export businesses.

Minmetals Development Co., Ltd imports and exports metals and minerals. The Company imports rolled steel, ore sand, and steel billets, and exports coke, coal, iron, bolognian stones, and other minerals.  Minmetals Development also provides freight transportation service and manages hotels.

Zhejiang Guyuelongshan Shaoxing Wine Co., Ltd. manufactures and markets yellow wines, white spirits, beverages, food, and food materials.  Through its subsidiaries, the Company also manufactures spandex and provides food services.

Hisense Visual Technology Co., Ltd. manufactures and markets electronic products and household electrical appliances. The Company produces television sets, refrigerators, freezers, communication products. Hisense Visual Technology conducts business in China.

SDIC Capital Co.,Ltd operates finance investment and management businesses. The Company focuses on securities, trust, fund, futures, insurance, and other finance areas. SDIC Capital also conducts investment banking and other self operation businesses.

China Resources Double-Crane Pharmaceutical Co., Ltd. develops, manufactures and markets a variety of medical products.  The Company's products include anti-influenza,  antihypertensives, and antibiotics.

Anhui Wanwei Updated High-Tech Material Industry Co.,Ltd manufactures and distributes chemical products. The Company produces polyester chips, vinyl acetate, methyl acetate, polyvinyl butyral, and polyvinyl alcohol fiber products. Anhui Wanwei Updated High-Tech Material Industry also conducts building materials production businesses.

Nanjing Gaoke Company Limited operates as a real estate development company. The Company develops and markets high-rise residential buildings, low-rise apartments, villas, commercial facilities, office buildings, and other related areas. Nanjing Gaoke also operates pharmaceutical manufacturing business.

Zhengzhou Yutong Bus Co.,Ltd. manufactures and distributes bus products. The Company produces coaches, city buses, school buses, airport airfield buses, and special vehicles. Zhengzhou Yutong Bus markets its products domestically and internationally.

Citychamp Dartong Co., Ltd. operates real estate businesses. The Company provides housing renovation, housing loans, real estate brokerage, and other services. Citychamp Dartong also operates special enameled wire manufacturing, new energy development, and other businesses.

China Gezhouba Group Company Limited provides infrastructure construction services. The Company provides new energy engineering construction, water resources and hydropower engineering construction, greening construction, and other related services. China Gezhouba Group also produces environmentally friendly materials.

Henan Yinge Industrial Investment Holding Co. Ltd. manufactures and distributes paper products. The Company produces household paper, cultural paper, packaging paper, paperboard, and specialty paper products. Henan Yinge Industrial Investment Holding markets its products domestically and internationally.

Zhejiang Furun Co., Ltd. produces and markets cotton fabric, woolen fabric, and spun silk products, as well as designs and manufactures garments.  The Company also sells pharmaceutical and healthcare products.  In addition, Zhejiang Furun operates toll roads.
Phenix Optical Co., Ltd. manufactures and markets a variety of optical and photographic products.  The Company's products include cameras, telescopes, optical lenses, and other related products.

CSSC Science & Technology Co., Ltd. designs and builds a variety of steel structures for buildings and transportation equipment. The Company also produces pressure containers, ship parts, electric equipment, and port machinery.
Shanghai Maling Aquarius Co., Ltd. manufactures and markets canned food, bottled water, flavorings, frozen food, and other related products.

Xinjiang Tianye Co., Ltd produces and sells chemical products. The Company manufactures and sells plastics, alkali, chlorine, and other products. Xinjiang Tianye also operates agricultural products production, goods delivery, and water and electricity distribution services.

Kangxin New Materials Co.,Ltd. operates in the wood industry. The Company designs, produces, and sells wood veneer and plywood products. Kangxin New Materials also participates in afforestation throughout China.

Sundy Land Investment Co., Ltd. engages in real estate developments, produces steel products. The company also engages in logistics, e-commerce, warehousing, processing and distribution, as well as supermarket sales.
Jiangsu Chengxing Phosph-Chemicals Co., Ltd. manufactures and markets phosphoric acid, phosphates, and other phosphoric chemicals.

Humanwell Healthcare (Group) Co.,Ltd. develops and sells pharmaceuticals. The Company manufactures and sells anesthetics, analgesics, central nerve system drugs, and other products. Humanwell Healthcare (Group) markets its products worldwide.

Ginwa Enterprise Group Inc., develops and manufactures biomedical products and health care products.  The Company also wholesales medicine and medical equipment as well as leases commercial properties and provides entertainment services.

Dongfeng Electronic Technology Co., Ltd. manufactures and markets motor vehicle parts and instruments including sensors, bearings, valves, and other related auto parts.  Through its subsidiaries, the Company also operates in automobiles and parts trading.

Tianjin Hi-Tech Development Co., Ltd. operates as a building materials sales company. The Company markets steel products and other products. Tianjin Hi-Tech Development also operates real estate sales, rental and leasing, and other businesses.

Jiangsu Boxin Investing & Holdings Co.,Ltd. design and develops artificial intelligence electronics. The Company produces smart phone, smart hardware device, electric toothbrush, beauty instrument, smart speaker, and children's smart watch products. Jiangsu Boxin Investing & Holdings also conducts cross-border e-commerce businesses.
CITIC Guoan Wine Co Ltd produces wines and other agricultural products. The company also develops and markets real estate properties.

Beijing Tongrentang Co., Ltd. develops, manufactures, and markets Chinese traditional medicines and medicinal wines.  The Company also operates pharmaceutical retail businesses and provides consulting services.
Eastern Gold Jade Co., Ltd. designs and processes jewelry products. The Company produces jades, gold bars, and other jewelries. Eastern Gold Jade also conducts internet financial businesses.
China Television Media, Ltd. produces television series and programs.  The Company also operates theme parks at its picture production sites, and provides advertising services.

TBEA Co., Ltd. manufactures and markets electrical components. The Company produces transformers, reactors, mutual inductors, and other products. TBEA also produces new energy equipment, new materials, and other products.

Xin Jiang Ready Health Industry Co., Ltd. manufactures and sells Chinese, anti-biotic, and bio-pharmaceutical medicines and equipment. The Company also operates retail and wholesale outlets for health care supplements and consumer products.

Baotou Tomorrow Technology Co., Ltd. manufactures caustic soda, PVC resin, phenol, hydrochloric acid, sulfuric acid, hydrofluoric acid, calcium carbide and other chemical products. The Company also develops computer peripheral equipment and computer software.

Easysight Supply Chain Management also operates products factoring, block chains management, and other businesses. Easysight Supply Chain Management provides services in China.

Greattown Holdings Ltd. operates real estate businesses. The Company provides house sales, house loans, property management, and other services. Greattown Holdings also operates financial investment, paper manufacturing, and other businesses.

Shanghai Kaichuang Marine International Co., Ltd. is in the business of fishery, aquaculture, and marine products processing and trading.

Guangzhou Development Group Incorporated distributes coal products. The Company markets brown coal products, bituminous coal products, hard coal products, coking coal products, and other related products. Guangzhou Development Group also provides electricity generation services.
Linhai Co., Ltd. manufactures and markets motorcycles, mopeds, engines, forestry machinery, sprinkling machinery, logging machinery, fire protection machinery, and related parts.

Tsinghua Tongfang Co.,Ltd wholesales consumer electronics products. The Company sales Home computers, business computers, notebook products, servers, mobile internet terminals, and other products. Tsinghua Tongfang also provides system integration services.

Through its subsidiaries, the Company also produces alkali, electro-optical products, consumer fine chemicals, and pharmaceutical products, generates electricity, trades general merchandise, as well as provides forestry services.
SAIC Motor Corporation Ltd., through joint ventures, manufactures and markets automobiles and related parts and accessories.
Jiangsu Etern Co., Ltd. manufactures and markets telecommunication electrical cable, optical cable, copper wire, and other telecommunication products.

Chongqing Road & Bridge Co., Ltd provides infrastructure construction services. The Company provides highway construction, bridge construction, and other related services. Chongqing Road & Bridge also operates real estate development business.

Hubei Mailyard Share Co., Ltd. produces and markets a wide range of garments. The Company's main products include suits, fashion garments, and knitwear series.  Mailyard also operates a hotel management business.

Sinolink Securities Co., Ltd. operates securities businesses. The Company provides securities brokerage, asset management, fixed income, equity investment, and investment banking services. Sinolink Securities also conducts investment consulting and asset custody businesses.

Nuode Investment Co., Ltd. develops, manufactures, and distributes copper materials.. The Company produces lithium ion battery copper foils and other lithium battery materials. Nuode Investment also manufactures and sells cables and wires.

China Northern Rare Earth (Group) High-Tech Co.,Ltd manufactures rare earth products. The Company produces rare earth concentrates, rare earth metals, rare earth oxides, new rare earth materials, and other products. China Northern Rare Earth (Group) High-Tech also operates import and export businesses.

The Company's products include high and low voltage circuit breakers, tap changers, relay protection equipment, switch equipment, and control equipment. It also designs, develops, manufactures, and sells wind power generation equipment.

Zhe Jiang Dong Ri Limited Company manufactures and produces electric lighting fixtures and parts. The Company also develops and invests in real estate, provides market space rental services, engages in computer network development and property management.

NBTM New Materials Group Co., Ltd. designs, manufactures and markets powder metallurgical products. The Company's products include motorcycle parts, compressor parts, electric tool parts, automobile parts and other parts.

China Eastern Airlines Corporation Limited operates airline businesses. The Company provides passenger transport, air freight, air catering, and other related services. China Eastern Airlines conducts businesses worldwide.

Chongqing Three Gorges Water Conservancy & Electric Power Co., Ltd. generates and distributes hydroelectric power. The Company also manufactures water conservation products as well as provides installation and advertising services.

Xining Special Steel Co.,Ltd. manufactures and distributes special steel products. The Company produces carbon steel, carbon steel, composite steel, stainless steel, and more. Xining Special Steel provides its products for automobile, railway, ship, petrochemical, aerospace, and mining machinery areas.
China Spacesat Co., Ltd. develops and manufactures satellites and related products. The Company also operates retail stores, hotels, and travel properties .

Y.U.D. Yangtze River Investment Industry Co., Ltd. engages in logistics business. The Company provides cargo transportation, supply chain, cross border electronic commerce, and other logistics services. Y.U.D. Yangtze River Investment Industry also operates property management and leasing, labor services, and other businesses.

Zhejiang Orient Financial Holdings Group also provides finance leasing, real estate sales, and other services.

Zhengzhou Coal Industry & Electric Power also operates railway freight transportation, cargo handling, and other businesses.

Jiangsu Hongtu High Technology Co., Ltd sales consumer electronics products The Company markets laser audio and video products, computers, networking equipment, cables, communication equipment, and other related products. Jiangsu Hongtu High Technology also operates industrial manufacturing, real estate, internet finance, and other businesses.
Shanxi Lanhua Sci-Tech Venture Co., Ltd. produces and markets coal and fertilizers.

China Railway Tielong Container Logistics Co., Ltd. provides freight services. The Company offers special container transportation, railway freight, port logistics, and other services. China Railway Tielong Container Logistics also operates real estate development industry.

Hangzhou Iron & Steel Co., Ltd. manufactures and markets iron and steel products including cast iron, steel billets, and steel materials.  Through its subsidiaries, the Company also operates in utility businesses, develops computer software, as well as provides water treatment services.
Hunan Jinjian Cereals Industry Co., Ltd. manufactures, processes, and markets rice, flour, and cooking oil.  The Company also manufactures dairy and pharmaceutical products, and develops real estate.

Chongqing Taiji Industry (Group) Co., Ltd. manufactures and markets medicines, healthcare products, medical packing products, and medical instruments.  The Company also imports and exports Chinese medicine materials and medical packing materials.
Ningbo Bird Co., Ltd. manufactures and markets cellular phones, pagers, and solar batteries.  The Company sells its products domestically.

Chongqing Brewery Co., Ltd. manufactures and markets beer products.  The Company also produces medical preparations and capsules.

Sichuan Langsha Holding Co., Ltd. produces and markets socks for men, women, and children. The Company also produces wallets.

China CYTS Tours Holding Co., Ltd. provides travel information and arrangement services.  Through its subsidiaries, the Company also manufactures medical instrument, provides system integration services for the insurance industry, and develops real estate.

Sichuan Western Resources Holding Co.,Ltd. mines and distributes metal products. The Company produces copper, gold, silver, and other products. Sichuan Western Resources Holding also operates asset management, investment, and other businesses.

Shangying Global Co., Ltd. designs, manufactures, and distributes apparel. The company also manufactures and markets industrial plastics.
Changchun Yidong Clutch Co., Ltd. manufactures and markets a variety of automobile clutches.  The Company supplies its products to manufacturers of cars, buses, and farm vehicles.
Langfang Development Co. Ltd. operates metal distribution businesses. The Company sells steels and other metal materials. Langfang Development conducts businesses in China.

China CSSC Holdings Ltd. offers shipbuilding, ship components, ship repairing and diesel engines manufacturing. The Company distributes its products within the domestic market and to overseas markets.

Shanghai Aerospace Automobile Electromechanical Co., Ltd. manufactures and markets automobile air conditioners, sensors, antennae, and other auto parts. The Company also researches and develops aerospace and solar energy.

Polaris Bay Group Co., Ltd. operates securities businesses. The Company provides securities brokerage, securities investment consulting, investment banking, credit trading, asset management, and other services. Polaris Bay Group also offers polyvinyl chloride pipe manufacturing services.
Hunan Huasheng Co., Ltd. manufactures and sells ramie textile products including ramie cloth and yarn.

Wintime Energy Co.,Ltd. offers coal operation services. The Company mines and processes raw coal, washed coal, and other coal chemicals. Wintime Energy also conducts power generation, petroleum trade, new energy, investment, and logistics businesses.

China Sports Industry Group Co., Ltd. manufactures, processes and sells sporting goods.  The company also involves in the development and sales of property, construction and operation of sports stadiums and sports facilities.

Zhejiang Juhua Co. Ltd. manufactures and markets chemical products.  The Company's products include alkali products, fluoride products, ammonia products, acid products, pesticides, biochemicals, and other chemical products.
